SUBTOPIC-ranger^#^
Command: craft

SYNOPSIS
	Ranger skill

DESCRIPTION
	This command enables the ranger to craft a bow. A ranger must
        find some good wood to be able to craft a fine bow.

        Arrows and bolts can also be crafted, but wood and
        an arrow head of some type must be found.

        Note that arrows must be placed inside a quiver for
        ease of drawing them during combat.

